---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<p class="hero-intro">Hi, I'm Dustin.</p>
			<h1>I build design cultures. I raise the craft bar. I still make things.</h1>
			<p>
				20+ years at T-Mobile, MoxiWorks, and Microsoft. I build teams that ship great work and grow as people. And I stay close enough to the craft to know the difference.
			</p>
			<p>
				When teams feel trusted, clear, and supported, they do their best work. I've led through ambiguity, reorgs, and high-pressure launches by bringing clarity to complex problem spaces and keeping the work grounded in real users and real business outcomes. I'm calm under pressure, direct in feedback, and invested in helping designers grow into the next version of themselves.
			</p>
			<p>
				No ego. Thoughtful direction. I don't always have all the answers, but I'll ask the right questions and help the team find the path forward.
			</p>
			<p>
				<a href="/work">Work</a> &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; <a href="/about">About</a> &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/dustinmartinka" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
			</p>
			<p class="tagline"><small>Be a good human. Do great things.</small></p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
